    <item>
      <title>特朗普对封口费判决提出上诉，开启新一轮法律战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-appeals-hush-money-verdict-kicking-off-fresh-legal-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统对纽约封口费案的有罪判决正式提起上诉，引发了一场新的法律战。在特朗普就职前几天，美国最高法院拒绝撤销对他的定罪判决，这场法律战不可避免地随之而来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-appeals-hush-money-verdict-kicking-off-fresh-legal-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 18:17:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
